last_episode_to_air.name: Cold Drop
last_episode_to_air.overview: The crew scrambles when a cold front threatens to turn into a crisis, and things heat up for Biel and Jésica once more. Patricia makes a surprising move.

name: Breathless
overview: A passionate medical team is devoted to saving lives in a bustling public hospital where tensions — and romance — keep their pulses racing.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Joaquín Sorolla is much more than a public hospital in Valencia where lives are saved on a daily basis. Doctors and residents work hard in the frenetic pace of the emergency room, where tensions, emotions and even desire accelerate the hearts of a staff who live increasingly on the edge. The arrival of a distinguished patient highlights the complicated situation of the public health system, lighting the fuse for what is to become an unprecedented and drastic strike.

episodes.name: Above All Else
episodes.overview: Joaquín Sorolla public hospital admits a notable patient. An overdose hits close to home for Pilar, while Rodri treats a child in distress.

episodes.name: Doctor Material
episodes.overview: Rodri's troubles escalate. Biel confronts Jésica about her relationship with Lluís. Meanwhile, Leo and May clash over a victim of a sexual assault.

episodes.name: We Stop
episodes.overview: Jésica faces the unimaginable as protests erupt at the hospital. Néstor struggles to get along with Patricia. Leo and Lluís find themselves in a dilemma.

episodes.name: I Trust You
episodes.overview: Patricia agrees to proceed with the expedited surgery. Jésica breaks down. The strike compels team members to take unthinkable actions.

episodes.name: Strike
episodes.overview: Pilar takes charge at the hospital as the strike puts Néstor and Patricia under pressure. Quique embraces his feelings, while Biel faces disappointment.

episodes.name: Last Man Standing
episodes.overview: A prison fire creates a frenzy in the ER. While Biel and Jésica's relationship becomes muddled, Patricia and Néstor agree to meet face-to-face on TV.

episodes.name: Scorched Earth
episodes.overview: The consequences of the strike put Néstor's career in the line of fire. May's water breaks at her worst moment with Rocío.

episodes.name: Cold Drop
episodes.overview: The crew scrambles when a cold front threatens to turn into a crisis, and things heat up for Biel and Jésica once more. Patricia makes a surprising move.
